#1. Personalized Greeting: Write a program that asks for the user's name and age. Then, print a message that says: #"Hello, [name]! You will be [age + 1] next year."

name = input('What is your name?')
age  = input('What is your age?')

print('Hello ', name, ' you will be ', int(age) + 1, ' in one year.')
